rows.label: tlk41700161_01_msg0001
rows.name:
You were the passengers on board that
ship from Superbia, weren't you?

rows.label: tlk41700161_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Are you heading to Iyasaki?
You'll need to pass through one
of the cloudways then.

rows.label: tlk41700161_01_msg0003
rows.name:
There are two paths you could take.
Lud Cloudway's the closer one, but the
route's full of dangerous monsters.

rows.label: tlk41700161_01_msg0004
rows.name:
If I were you, I'd take Orl Cloudway
instead. Once you reach Baldotas Isle,
head for Daram Isle to get there.
